codex
I’ve narrowed the fix to the execution route rather than the vulnerability logic: use a public Balancer flashloan for minimal WETH funding, post `cETH` collateral, borrow the reporter-backed debt at constructor price `1`, dump it through the oracle’s own configured anchor pool, then redeem nearly all collateral to realize profit and repay.
